OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright spells initially,
OL,6,Fbut becoming generally cloudy with a
OL,7,Ffew light showers possible, though
OL,8,Fmost places likely remaining dry.
OL,9,FSunnier spells may develop later in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Winds generally light
OL,11,Fbut breezier towards the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells going into the
OL,14,Fevening and becoming cool. Patchy low
OL,15,Fcloud may develop towards the coast
OL,16,Fand spread further inland later, with
OL,17,Fa few misty patches possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
