OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA bright day with mainly fine,
OL,6,Fdry weather and light winds. Plenty of
OL,7,Fsunny spells initially, but sunshine
OL,8,Fperhaps becoming hazy during the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Risk of patchy rain
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,13,Fand often cloudy during this period,
OL,14,Fwith outbreaks of rain at times. The
OL,15,Fbest of any sunshine perhaps on
OL,16,FThursday. Gradually turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
